	(170, 'api/v1/pages', 'post', '{"Host":"localhost:8000","Connection":"keep-alive","Content-Length":"5183","Accept":"application\\/json, text\\/javascript, *\\/*; q=0.01","X-Requested-With":"XMLHttpRequest","User-Agent":"Mozilla\\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\\/87.0.4280.88 Safari\\/537.36","Content-Type":"application\\/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8","Origin":"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000","Sec-Fetch-Site":"same-origin","Sec-Fetch-Mode":"cors","Sec-Fetch-Dest":"empty","Referer":"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/admin\\/paginas\\/editar\\/102","Accept-Encoding":"gzip, deflate, br","Accept-Language":"en-US,en;q=0.9,es;q=0.8","Cookie":"wp-settings-time-1=1602517688; _ga=GA1.1.1170798641.1603546866; debug-bar-theme=light; debug-bar-tab=ci-files; debug-bar-state=minimized; ci_session=11bvvrg2jboodo1hjbcin19j0fltf4s6","title":"TypeScript: The Best Resources to Learn It","subtitle":"","path":"typescript-the-best-resources-to-learn-it","page_type_id":"1","status":"2","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>If you are interested in learning&nbsp;<a href=\\"https:\\/\\/javarevisited.blogspot.com\\/2018\\/07\\/top-5-courses-to-learn-typescript.html\\">TypeScript&nbsp;<\\/a>or&nbsp;<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.java67.com\\/2018\\/01\\/top-5-free-angular-js-online-courses-for-web-developers.html\\">Angular<\\/a>, one of the popular JavaScript frameworks for developing front-end, which uses TypeScript and looking for some resources like books, tutorials and courses then you have come to the right place.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>In this article, I am going to share some of the&nbsp;<strong>best, free TypeScript online courses<\\/strong>&nbsp;you can use to learn this powerful programming language.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>For those who don\\u2019t know TypeScript, it\\u2019s a new dynamically typed programming language from Microsoft which augments&nbsp;<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.java67.com\\/2018\\/04\\/top-5-free-javascript-courses-to-learn.html\\">JavaScript\\u2019s<\\/a>&nbsp;programming syntax by adding some new features which help in object-oriented application development, particularly introduction of Types.<br><br>As the name suggests,&nbsp;<strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>&nbsp;is a combination of Types and&nbsp;<a href=\\"https:\\/\\/medium.com\\/javarevisited\\/my-favorite-free-tutorials-and-courses-to-learn-javascript-8f4d0a71faf2\\">JavaScript<\\/a>, which means now you have proper variables in your code like a String or Integer variable and fewer type-safety related bugs to worry.<br><br>The good thing about TypeScript is that it compiles into native&nbsp;<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.java67.com\\/2017\\/07\\/6-ways-to-redirect-web-page-using-JavaScript-and-jQuery.html\\">JavaScript code<\\/a>&nbsp;which can run on a browser, which means you now have a better syntax to write code and you can also take advantage of the ubiquitousness of JavaScript.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list {\\"ordered\\":true} -->\\n<ol><li>Introduction to&nbsp;<strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>. ...<\\/li><li><strong>Typescript<\\/strong>&nbsp;Fundamentals. ...<\\/li><li>Getting Started with&nbsp;<strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>. ...<\\/li><li><strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>&nbsp;Fast Crash Course. ...<\\/li><li><strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>&nbsp;Design Patterns. ...<\\/li><li><strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>, Quick and Easy. ...<\\/li><li><strong>Typescript<\\/strong>&nbsp;with modern React (i.e. hooks, context, suspense) ...<\\/li><li>The Complete&nbsp;<strong>TypeScript<\\/strong>&nbsp;For Beginners.<\\/li><\\/ol>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->","page_id":"102","publishondate":"true","date_publish":"","visibility":"1","template":"default","layout":"default","categorie_id":"0","subcategorie_id":"0","mainImage":"1285","page_data":{"title":"TypeScript: The Best Resources to Le